<td style="width:12%; background:#FFFFE0; border:solid 2px #F2F2F3; border-bottom:solid 1px #F9F9F9"><a href="/wiki/Portal:Hinduism/What%27s_Hinduism" title="Portal:Hinduism/What&#39;s Hinduism"><span style="color:black;">What is Hinduism?</span></a>
</td>
<td style="width:4%">
</td>
<td style="width:12%; background:#FFFFE0; border:solid 3px #F2F2F3; border-bottom:solid 1px #F9F9F9"><a href="/wiki/Portal:Hinduism/Indices" title="Portal:Hinduism/Indices"><span style="color:black;">Indices</span></a>
